  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/16afaed7feeb61b01f1785cd819b5c55.poster.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/16afaed7feeb61b01f1785cd819b5c55.webm?t=1772070985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/16afaed7feeb61b01f1785cd819b5c55.mp4?t=1772070985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Sailing alone:Aftermath》is a post-apocalyptic nautical survival game where players find themselves in a harsh, open-world, navigating through endless oceans, exploring countless islands and lands, engaging in battles with dangerous creatures, searching for submerged treasures, visiting docks, harbors, and towns, encountering a diverse array of NPCs, and playing any role you desire - warrior, merchant, explorer, treasure hunter, pirate, pirate hunter, cargo captain, dockworker, and more.<br><br><strong>Special features：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/a24c74664aa1158647f4d097084c77dc.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br>● A variety of shipboard modules can be customized and combined to match various functions of vessels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/75dd37994c805b756857da42ac2be289.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br>● Weapons of various qualities come with different random entries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/80bc05cdcdad9af7ec793652ce8d1036.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br>●Customizable Character<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/423dab7f053fa2891c6ae6a45a7a7400.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br>●Customizable Land Vehicles<br><br><strong>and:</strong><br>●A completely seamless and infinite open world<br>●Dynamic Day-Night Cycle and Weather System<br>●Freely Buildable Facilities in the Cabin of Ship<br>●Customizable Character Upgrade Path<br>●A Variety of Craftable Items<br>●Pirate Encounters and Naval Battles",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/16afaed7feeb61b01f1785cd819b5c55.poster.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/16afaed7feeb61b01f1785cd819b5c55.webm?t=1772070985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/16afaed7feeb61b01f1785cd819b5c55.mp4?t=1772070985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Sailing alone:Aftermath》is a post-apocalyptic nautical survival game where players find themselves in a harsh, open-world, navigating through endless oceans, exploring countless islands and lands, engaging in battles with dangerous creatures, searching for submerged treasures, visiting docks, harbors, and towns, encountering a diverse array of NPCs, and playing any role you desire - warrior, merchant, explorer, treasure hunter, pirate, pirate hunter, cargo captain, dockworker, and more.<br><br><strong>Special features：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/a24c74664aa1158647f4d097084c77dc.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br>● A variety of shipboard modules can be customized and combined to match various functions of vessels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/75dd37994c805b756857da42ac2be289.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br>● Weapons of various qualities come with different random entries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/80bc05cdcdad9af7ec793652ce8d1036.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br>●Customizable Character<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990530/extras/423dab7f053fa2891c6ae6a45a7a7400.avif?t=1772070985\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br>●Customizable Land Vehicles<br><br><strong>and:</strong><br>●A completely seamless and infinite open world<br>●Dynamic Day-Night Cycle and Weather System<br>●Freely Buildable Facilities in the Cabin of Ship<br>●Customizable Character Upgrade Path<br>●A Variety of Craftable Items<br>●Pirate Encounters and Naval Battles",
